wineberry
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:also called makomako a small tree or shrub notable for its clusters of berries. <i>Aristotelea serrata</i> (formerly <i>A. racemosa</i>), =MAKOMAKO n2, =(NEW ZEALAND) CURRANT
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
