Vol / Page: 50
Edition:
Quote: <i>Aristotelia serrata</i> (J.R. & G. Forst.) Oliv. Common name: <i>Wineberry </i> Maori name: Makomako ... This handsome shrub is common on bush burns and the outskirts of forests. ...It was known as <i>A. racemosa</i> (A.Cunn.) Hook.f. but the Forsters' name has priority.
